    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hi @dcossey014 - thanks for your report. The readline functionality in IPython 5.x and newer is handled by [python-prompt-toolkit](https://github.com/jonathanslenders/python-prompt-toolkit), so there are lots of little things like that which are not yet implemented in prompt toolkit's vi mode. \n\nAs a die hard vi mode user, I must say that it's rather painful to use IPython now, and I haven't had the chance to make contributions backt o prompt-toolkit to make this better. \n"
